---
title: Smart Chipotle Glazed Pork Chops with Warm Green Bean Potato Salad
description: BBQ chipotle-glazed pork chops get nicely charred under the broiler to give this dish sweet-smoky heat. It's paired with a warm potato salad with crunchy pickles and green beans.
